relatedArticles.headline: Revealed: England and Netherlands' expected XIs for tonight's Euro 2024 semi-final - with Gareth Southgate making a big call on the left-hand side
relatedArticles.previewText: According sources close to the camp, Southgate is expected to stick with the system England used during their quarter-final win over Switzerland when they face the Netherlands in the last four.

relatedArticles.headline: Alice Evans is a 'total nightmare' and 'out of control'. Friends of Ioan Gruffudd tell KATIE HIND his side of the story, reveal the truth about the Rolex row... and brand his 'cruel' ex's claims of poverty 'just nonsense'
relatedArticles.previewText: When Ioan Gruffudd's fiancee Bianca Wallace posted a picture of herself wearing a new Rolex watch, little did she know it would spark such a massive row.

relatedArticles.headline: Dutch hooligans injure five England fans 'after trying to steal St George's flag' in series of attacks on Dortmund bars as sickening violence mars build up to Euros semi-final
relatedArticles.previewText: Videos have surfaced on X of swaths of people dressed in the iconic bright orange football shirts throwing stools and benches outside a local cafe ahead of the semi-final match tonight.

relatedArticles.headline: NETHERLANDS vs ENGLAND PLAYER RATINGS: Who has been easily Gareth Southgate's most consistent performer? Which 6/10 star hasn't done enough on the ball for the Three Lions? And which Dutch players have lacked chemistry?
relatedArticles.previewText: Mail Sport's CRAIG HOPE and MATT BARLOW run the rule over Koeman and Southgate's teams, and assess who comes up trumps ahead of Wednesday evening's kick-off.

previewText: Follow Mail Sport's live blog for the latest score, team news and updates as England take on the Netherlands from the BVB Stadion in Dortmund.
